  Text: |+
    Slide 9.  Editor Button Icons - Intro 
     [Show editor buttons comparison]
    
    > Now let’s take a step back and let’s go deeper into the layout comparison 
    
    > If you are familiar with Unity, and when I say familiar - I mean not even that 10 years of experience as a Unity dev, let's say you just know how the engine works. 
    
    > Besides 1 window in particular, which is the preview window
    Your learning curve for this will be very low 
    
