  Text: |
    Slide 2. Why 
    [Show “Why”]
    
    > I’d love to provide you with my personal experience as a unity developer. I’ll show you that here. 
    
    > Built for AR - if you are goal is building AR experience, this tool was created for you 
    
    > Is speed important for us? What kind of use cases are we tackling as developers?
    
    > Why wouldn’t test every platform before making a final decision and invest so much time into learning an app 

