- !<Text/dec29324-24de-4f95-8f77-4a73da3bf78a>
  PrefabRemaps:
    []
  Name: Text
  Enabled: true
  RenderOrder: 0
  StretchMode: Stretch
  VerticalAlignment: Top
  HorizontalAlignment: Left
  MeshShadowMode: None
  ShadowColor: {x: 1.000000, y: 1.000000, z: 1.000000, w: 1.000000}
  ShadowDensity: 1.000000
  Text: |
    Slide 15.  Pre QnA > Resources 
    
    [Show Resources and how to get them]
    
    > I hope this guide was insightful for you to get you started. (Flip up your specs-eye contact)
    
    >Generally, we noticed how Unity developers put together a full competitive project and became relatively comfortable with Lens Studio in as little as 2 days of work. 
    
    > Atley showed you the potential of Spectacles, Karen and our amazing partners showed you what’s possible on spectacles, and finally I hope I provide you enough resources to get started!
    
    >We are so excited to have you here with us, we aim to empower you and give you the tools to unlock what we cannot. 
    
    > Remember to connect with us and our community for development support.
    
    > Join me in welcoming back our outstanding speaker as we dive into our final Q&A session and Let’s build the future together. 

