  ShadowDensity: 1.000000
  Text: |-
    Slide 14.  Material: Shaders
    [Show Editor Graph]
    
    > Every material has its own shader. 
    
    > You can edit materials using the inspectors or  Material editor which you might think of it as the Unity’s ShaderGraph 
    
    > In Unity you can edit shaders using HLSL - GLSL
    
    > In Lens studio you can edit material editor nodes via custom Node Code 
